= display_search_boxes('articles')

.row-fluid
  .landing_main.span8

    .title Articles

    = render partial: '/datasource_warning', locals: {warning: warning}


    %p Searches a large database of mostly full-text journal articles.

    %p For scholarly articles in the:
    %ul
      %li Humanities and Social Sciences, try #{link_to 'Ebscohost Research Databases', 'http://www.columbia.edu/cgi-bin/cul/resolve?clio6329559'} or #{link_to 'ProQuest', 'http://www.columbia.edu/cgi-bin/cul/resolve?clio8557099'}
      %li Sciences, try #{link_to 'Web of Science', 'http://www.columbia.edu/cgi-bin/cul/resolve?clio2054244'} or #{link_to 'Scopus', 'http://www.columbia.edu/cgi-bin/cul/resolve?clio6273999'}
      %li 18<sup>th</sup> and 19<sup>th</sup> centuries, try #{link_to 'American Periodicals', 'http://www.columbia.edu/cgi-bin/cul/resolve?ARS2786'} or #{link_to 'British Periodicals', 'http://www.columbia.edu/cgi-bin/cul/resolve?clio6022732'}

    %p Use #{datasource_switch_link('Databases', 'databases')} to browse all of our databases by subject.

    %p To see a list of resources by subject, consult our subject guides.

